# Repo CODEOWNERS — used to auto-assign reviewers on PRs.
#
# The weekly content-audit workflow (.github/workflows/weekly-content-audit.md)
# opens PRs against these paths; CODEOWNERS handles reviewer assignment so the
# workflow itself does not need to request reviewers.

*                            @ms-mfg-community/maintainers

# Content registry + generated audit artefacts
/docs/_meta/                 @ms-mfg-community/maintainers
/labs/                       @ms-mfg-community/maintainers

# Agentic workflows + supporting config
/.github/workflows/          @ms-mfg-community/maintainers
/.github/agents/             @ms-mfg-community/maintainers
/.github/prompts/            @ms-mfg-community/maintainers
/mcp-configs/                @ms-mfg-community/maintainers
